n證監條例，發寒商只可以賺16個溢價<br />\n必須按金額做足對沖<br />\n白天鵝黑天鵝，發寒商都要硬食<br />\n<br />\n所以部分索性執柒佐佢算！"},{"pid":"bd93d99011649d5e36d0264d8008e26df9dddede","tid":486140,"uid":68728,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T08:00:31.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>打穿埋$350個重貨區，少左人撈底先可能跌停<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n打穿350，殺盡牛仔，然後一升冇回頭，逼散戶再高追，跟手爆煲，騰訊從此變成一隻公用股</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n即時諗起941<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n每個大牛市都有一兩隻總龍頭，全部命運都係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n941， 2628, 330, 494, 5 又可嘗唔係曾經一時的明日之星<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n認真問~你講過5隻<br />\n當時業務有冇而家既700咁屈機?</blockquote><br />\n吹到會相同命運<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n除非有日全世界唔再上網唔再打機，咁就真係可能由400蚊跌到40蚊</blockquote><br />\n吹到不死咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日中共一個政策改變 可以即刻一切都化為烏有"},{"pid":"9ee4eb990644eeb510eddc494a0563a22adede47","tid":486140,"uid":63934,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T13:04:28.000Z","msg":"根本就係物極必反<br />\n成班賭徒想短時間買高槓桿野發達<br />\n邊有咁著數<br />\n一定洗走你地先再升突"},{"pid":"1a3ae49c9dcd7a61e0f91b05b8134593800c2923","tid":486140,"uid":67280,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T13:28:08.000Z","msg":"關咩事，以前冇牛熊咩又係跌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n大戶覺得利差夠咪推跌佢，大戶日日推3-4蚊，你老散日日幫大戶推上6-7蚊又屌人做價<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fbcd34f281bb4a7bbfd5725eddc4e9869b0842f9","tid":486140,"uid":34896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-02T13:51:17.000Z","msg":"諗起之前個post有條友死都話唔會有大戶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03b552b726ada007130c69b1